  "text": "Therefore, \u03c7 \u03bb (\u00b5) = P\u03bb(\u03c7 w 1 (\u00b5), . . . , \u03c7 w r (\u00b5)) , (1.2) for all \u00b5 \u2208 P k + (g). Define the fusion matrices N \u03bb by Verlinde's formula [CITATION_1] :",
